snippet.textDisplay: Well, I think of all of the people who have many fond memories of the classic games, in particular Mega Man 2.  Face it, the series hasn't changed much in twenty years, and not surprisingly this has turned a lot of people away, who have simply become bored of the same thing over and over again--and it's understandable, sure.  But when it comes down to the music, I have nothing but extraordinarily high praise for the Zero series and the ZX series, and I'm just disappointed that it's so unknown.
snippet.textOriginal: Well, I think of all of the people who have many fond memories of the classic games, in particular Mega Man 2.  Face it, the series hasn't changed much in twenty years, and not surprisingly this has turned a lot of people away, who have simply become bored of the same thing over and over again--and it's understandable, sure.  But when it comes down to the music, I have nothing but extraordinarily high praise for the Zero series and the ZX series, and I'm just disappointed that it's so unknown.
